国务院成立泉州酒店塌陷事故调查组。
State Council set up Quanzhou Hotel collapse investigation team.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 戴越澎湃新闻从应急管理部获悉，3月7日19时5分许，福建省泉州市鲤城区欣佳酒店发生楼体坍塌事故，造成29人死亡、42人受伤。
A news report from the Ministry of Emergency Management said 29 people were killed and 42 injured when the building collapsed at the Xinjia Hotel in Yicheng District, Quanzhou City, Fujian Province, at about 19.05 March.
依据《生产安全事故报告和调查处理条例》（国务院令第493号）有关规定，国务院决定成立福建省泉州市欣佳酒店“3·7”坍塌事故调查组并开展调查工作。
In accordance with the Regulations on Reporting and Handling Production Safety Accidents (State Council Decree No. 493), the State Council has decided to set up the Investigation Team for the March 7 collapse of Xinjia Hotel Quanzhou City, Fujian Province.
国务院安委会办公室副主任付建华任组长。
Vice Director of Security Committee of State Council Fu Jianhua.
福建省泉州市鲤城区人民政府通报，3月7日19:30左右，鲤城区欣佳酒店发生楼体坍塌，截至3月12日11时15分，事故造成29人死亡。
The people's government of Lei Cheng, Quanzhou City, Fujian Province, reported that 29 people had died in the collapse of the Xinjia Hotel in Lei Cheng on March 7 at about 1930 hours.
澎湃新闻注意到，在3月11日泉州市政府召开的新闻发布会上，福建泉州市政府常务副市长洪自强介绍，经初步调查，欣佳酒店在建设、改造和审批等方面存在严重问题。
On March 11, 2008, Hong Zhiqiang, vice mayor of Quanzhou City, Fujian Province, was briefed by the Quanzhou government at a news conference held by the Quanzhou government on March 11.
已经将相关证据收集固化，对相关责任人员采取强制措施、财产保全措施。
Relevant evidence has been collected and solidified, and coercive measures and property preservation measures have been taken against those responsible.
初步调查情况上交上级调查组。
The preliminary investigation is referred to the superior investigation team.
此前，在3月10日国务院联防联控机制举行的新闻发布会上，应急管理部副部长尚勇也表示，经初步了解，这是一起安全生产责任事故，事故酒店系违法建设，多次违规改建，“暴露出地方有关方面安全生产监管责任不落实，长期造成安全风险隐患的漏洞和盲区，应该说血的教训令人震惊。
At a press conference held on March 10 by the State Council's joint defense and control mechanism, Shang Yong, deputy minister of emergency management, also said that, based on preliminary knowledge, the accident hotel was illegally built and rebuilt several times illegally.
”他表示，待救援基本结束后，将全面开展事故调查，迅速查明原因，严格依法依规追究事故责任人相关责任，包括法律责任。
He said that when the rescue work was basically over, an investigation into the accident would be carried out, the cause would be promptly found out and the relevant responsibilities of the party responsible for the accident, including legal responsibility, would be strictly followed according to law.
本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
